    <item>
      <title>Robinhood 拟以 3 亿美元收购 TradePMR，以推动财富客户发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/robinhood-to-buy-tradepmr-for-300-million-in-wealth-client-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗宾汉市场公司 (Robinhood Markets Inc.) 同意收购 TradePMR，这是一家为注册投资顾问提供的托管和投资组合管理平台，因为这家在线经纪公司试图瞄准更广泛的富裕投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/robinhood-to-buy-tradepmr-for-300-million-in-wealth-client-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油供应过剩将阻碍特朗普“水力压裂、水力压裂、水力压裂”的号召</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/oil-glut-set-to-thwart-trump-s-call-to-frack-frack-frack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的“水力压裂、水力压裂、水力压裂”誓言即将与全球原油过剩局面发生冲突，而全球原油过剩局面最终将抑制页岩油产量创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/oil-glut-set-to-thwart-trump-s-call-to-frack-frack-frack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国国防部长将波罗的海电缆泄露事件视为破坏行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/german-defense-chief-sees-cable-breaches-in-baltic-as-sabotage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托利斯表示，波罗的海两条海底数据电缆受损事件必须作为破坏行为进行调查，并指出俄罗斯对欧盟构成了混合威胁和军事威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/german-defense-chief-sees-cable-breaches-in-baltic-as-sabotage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 10:30:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
